PresentationColumn.name: Last Activity Description
PresentationColumn.Description:
The description of the last activity.
The last activity is the Activity with the most recent start date, where the activity is set to done and the start date is in the past.

PresentationColumn.name: Last Activity Date
PresentationColumn.Description: The start date of the last activity. The last activity is the Activity with the most recent start date, where the activity is set to done and the start date is in the past.

PresentationColumn.name: Next Open Activity Description
PresentationColumn.Description: The description of the next activity. The next open activity is the Activity with the earliest start date, when the activity is not set to 'Done' or 'Closed' or 'Completed' and where the activity start date is after 01/04/2012.
